<h1>Post</h1>

<p>I'm totally stealing this content from the <a href="http://blogs.coldfusion.com">official ColdFusion blog</a>, but as it is good news I think I'm allowed. The ColdFusion Summit, a ColdFusion conference organized by Adobe's ColdFusion team, is now officially announced. Details:</p>
<p>October 24th and 25th</p>
<p><a href="http://www.mandalaybay.com/">Manadalay Bay Resort &amp; Casino</a>, Las Vegas, Nevada</p>
<p>Registration cost: $250</p>
<p>Each paid registration will receive a FREE copy of ColdFusion Builder (MSRP value of $299!)</p>
